name: build-a-bear stuffing
description: limply thrust until neither of you achieve orgasm. in the twilight of a failing marriage. under the indifferent gaze of an overpriced bear in a Harley Davidson vest. who has lived a happier life than you ever could. collecting dust on the piece of shit self it sits on. allow the fading neon glow of the sign to soundtrack your failing organs. and buy a bear to replenish another landfill.
